embeds.title: Meme Posting Guidelines
embeds.description: We all love memes, but there are some that we feel should not exist within this server.

fields.name: Please don't post the following types of meme:
fields.value:
- Suicide/Self Harm 
 - National/International tragedies 
 - Racist content 
 - Pedophilia 
 - Violent or graphic content 
 - Politically charged content 
 - Animal abuse 
 - Depictions of bodily fluids 
 - Homophobic content 
 
 For more information please re-read <#217150582190768128>. 
 **Still not sure about your post? Feel free to ask a staff member in DM.**
